    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sites considered in the past or present as consecrated or important to a deity or a religion; sites include natural features, such as springs and caves, as well as sites upon which built works have been constructed, such as standing stones and pilgrimage churches.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
